'''IT Territory''' (Russian: Территория ИТ) is a Russian company, which is specialized in developing and publishing MMO's. They published [[The Lord of the Rings Online]] in Russia and maintain its' servers ([[Fornost#Portrayal in Adaptations|Fornost]] and [[Mirkwood#Portrayal in Adaptations|Mirkwood]]).<ref>{{webcite|author=William Dobson|articleurl=http://massively.joystiq.com/2009/04/23/lord-of-the-rings-online-launches-in-korea-and-russia/|articlename=Lord of the Rings Online launches in Korea and Russia|dated=23 April 2009|website=Massively|accessed=2 January 2012}}</ref>
